View shadow git edit history

Usage: normalize history [OPTIONS] [FILE]

Arguments:
  [FILE]  Filter history to specific file

Options:
  -r, --root <ROOT>    Root directory (defaults to current directory)
      --all            Show full tree structure (all branches)
      --status         Show uncommitted shadow edits since last git commit
      --diff <REF>     Show diff for a specific commit
  -n, --limit <LIMIT>  Maximum number of entries to show [default: 20]
      --prune <KEEP>   Prune shadow history, keeping only the last N commits
      --json           Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>      Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty         Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact        Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help           Print help
